The paper deals with query intent discovery, which is a problem in database systems. Therefore, cs.DB is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses probabilistic abduction models and semantic similarity, which are techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques.
